Exception:

Checked Exception: Error happen during compile time. IOException
Unchecked Exception: Error happen during runtime. NullPointerException

Handling Exceptions:
- using Try Catch block to catch the exception before runtime, so runtime will not throw the exception. Inside the code/method
- Declaring Exception using throws someException , will cause runtime exception. after method declaretion before method body
- throw new someException() means it will deliberatly we are throwing exception. Inside the method